#: app/assets/javascripts/app/models/ticket_time_accounting_type.coffee
msgid ""
"**Activity Types** can be used to group the different ticket time accounting "
"entries together. For example, entries that are relevant to a \"Billing\" "
"type.\n"
"\n"
"When you enable the recording of the activity type, the users will be able "
"to select a type from this list. Additionally, a column with an associated "
"activity type will be rendered for an entry in the **Activity** table under "
"the **Accounted Time** tab."
msgstr ""
"**Jenis Aktivitas** dapat digunakan untuk mengelompokkan entri pencatatan "
"waktu tiket yang berbeda. Misalnya, entri yang relevan dengan jenis "
"\"Penagihan\".\n"
"\n"
"Ketika Anda mengaktifkan pencatatan jenis aktivitas, pengguna dapat memilih "
"jenis dari daftar ini. Selain itu, kolom dengan jenis aktivitas terkait akan "
"ditampilkan untuk entri di tabel **Aktivitas** di bawah tab **Waktu yang "
"Diperhitungkan**."

#: app/assets/javascripts/app/models/data_privacy_task.coffee
msgid ""
"**Data Privacy** helps you to delete and verify the removal of existing data "
"from the system.\n"
"\n"
"It can be used to delete tickets, organizations, and users. The owner "
"assignment will be unset in case the deleted user is an agent.\n"
"\n"
"Data Privacy tasks will be executed every 10 minutes. The execution might "
"take some additional time depending on the number of objects that will be "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"**Privasi Data** membantu Anda menghapus dan memverifikasi penghapusan data "
"yang ada dari sistem.\n"
"\n"
"Ini dapat digunakan untuk menghapus tiket, organisasi, dan pengguna. "
"Penugasan pemilik akan dibatalkan jika pengguna yang dihapus adalah agen.\n"
"\n"
"Tugas Privasi Data akan dijalankan setiap 10 menit. Eksekusi mungkin "
"memerlukan waktu tambahan tergantung pada jumlah objek yang akan dihapus."

#: app/assets/javascripts/app/models/sla.coffee
msgid ""
"**Service Level Agreements**, abbreviated **SLAs**, help you to meet "
"specific response times for your customers' requests. This way you can "
"define goals such as answering every inquiry within eight hours. If you are "
"at risk of missing this target, Zammad will alert you.\n"
"\n"
"You can define targets for three different metrics: **response time** (time "
"between the creation of a ticket and the first reaction of an agent), "
"**update time** (time between a customer's request and an agent's reaction), "
"and **solution time** (time between creating and closing a ticket).\n"
"\n"
"Any escalated tickets (i.e. tickets that have missed the defined target) are "
"displayed in a separate view in your overviews. You can also configure "
"**email notifications**."
msgstr ""
"**Perjanjian Tingkat Layanan**, disingkat **SLA**, membantu Anda memenuhi "
"waktu respons tertentu untuk permintaan pelanggan Anda. Dengan cara ini Anda "
"dapat menentukan tujuan seperti menjawab setiap pertanyaan dalam delapan "
"jam. Jika Anda berisiko melewatkan target ini, Zammad akan memberi tahu Anda."
"\n"
"\n"
"Anda dapat menentukan target untuk tiga metrik berbeda: **waktu respons** ("
"waktu antara pembuatan tiket dan reaksi pertama agen), **waktu pembaruan** ("
"waktu antara permintaan pelanggan dan reaksi agen), dan **waktu solusi** ("
"waktu antara pembuatan dan penutupan tiket).\n"
"\n"
"Semua tiket yang dieskalasi (yaitu tiket yang melewatkan target yang "
"ditentukan) ditampilkan dalam tampilan terpisah di ikhtisar Anda. Anda juga "
"dapat mengonfigurasi **notifikasi email**."

