"Mendefinisikan apakah konfigurasi alias penerima PGP diaktifkan atau tidak."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:685
msgid ""
"Defines if the agent has to accept a confirmation dialog when changing the "
"article visibility to \"public\"."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah agen harus menerima dialog konfirmasi saat mengubah "
"visibilitas artikel menjadi \"publik\"."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:77
msgid ""
"Defines if the application is in developer mode (all users have the same "
"password and password reset will work without email delivery)."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah aplikasi dalam mode pengembang (semua pengguna "
"memiliki kata sandi yang sama dan reset kata sandi akan berfungsi tanpa "
"pengiriman email)."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:6107
msgid ""
"Defines if the bubble menu feature of the richtext editor is enabled. Note "
"that this setting will be ignored if the writing assistant is turned on."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah fitur menu gelembung dari editor richtext diaktifkan. "
"Perhatikan bahwa pengaturan ini akan diabaikan jika asisten penulisan "
"diaktifkan."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:5941
msgid ""
"Defines if the change of the primary organization of a user will update the "
"100 most recent tickets for this user as well."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah perubahan organisasi utama pengguna akan memperbarui "
"100 tiket terbaru untuk pengguna ini juga."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:604
msgid ""
"Defines if the core workflow communication should run over ajax instead of "
"websockets."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah komunikasi core workflow harus berjalan melalui ajax "
"daripada websocket."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:630
msgid ""
"Defines if the email should be displayed in the result of the user/"
"organization widget."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah email harus ditampilkan dalam hasil widget pengguna/"
"organisasi."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4976
msgid ""
"Defines if the i-doit (https://www.i-doit.org/) integration is enabled or "
"not."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah integrasi i-doit (https://www.i-doit.org/) diaktifkan "
"atau tidak."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:2376
msgid ""
"Defines if the ticket conditions editor supports complex logical expressions."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah editor kondisi tiket mendukung ekspresi logis yang "
"kompleks."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:2402
msgid ""
"Defines if the ticket conditions editor supports regular expression "
"operators for triggers and ticket auto assignment."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah editor kondisi tiket mendukung operator ekspresi "
"reguler untuk trigger dan penugasan otomatis tiket."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4125
msgid "Defines if the time accounting types are enabled."
msgstr "Mendefinisikan apakah jenis akuntansi waktu diaktifkan."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:5857
msgid ""
"Defines if the two-factor authentication method authenticator app is enabled "
"or not."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah metode autentikasi dua faktor aplikasi autentikator "
"diaktifkan atau tidak."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:5825
msgid ""
"Defines if the two-factor authentication method security keys is enabled or "
"not."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan apakah metode autentikasi dua faktor kunci keamanan "
"diaktifkan atau tidak."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:3034
msgid "Defines if tickets can be created via web form."
msgstr "Mendefinisikan apakah tiket dapat dibuat melalui formulir web."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4515
msgid "Defines if tickets should be closed if service is recovered."
msgstr "Mendefinisikan apakah tiket harus ditutup jika layanan dipulihkan."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4367
msgid "Defines postmaster filter for filters managed via admin interface."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk filter yang dikelola melalui "
"antarmuka admin."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4277
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to check if email has been created by Zammad "
"itself and will set the article sender."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk memeriksa apakah email dibuat oleh "
"Zammad sendiri dan akan mengatur pengirim artikel."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4286
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to check if the email is a self-created "
"notification email, then ignore it to prevent email loops."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk memeriksa apakah email adalah email "
"notifikasi yang dibuat sendiri, lalu abaikan untuk mencegah email loop."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4313
msgid "Defines postmaster filter to handle secure mailing."
msgstr "Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk menangani email aman."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4430
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify Jira mails for correct follow-ups."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi email Jira untuk "
"tindak lanjut yang benar."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4412
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify ServiceNow mails for correct follow-"
"ups."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi email ServiceNow "
"untuk tindak lanjut yang benar."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4223
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify auto responses to prevent auto replies "
"from Zammad."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi respons otomatis "
"untuk mencegah balasan otomatis dari Zammad."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4241
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify follow-up ticket for merged tickets."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi tiket tindak lanjut "
"untuk tiket yang digabung."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4232
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify follow-ups (based on admin settings)."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi tindak lanjut ("
"berdasarkan pengaturan admin)."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4322
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify out-of-office emails for follow-up "
"detection and keeping current ticket state."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi email out-of-office "
"untuk deteksi tindak lanjut dan mempertahankan status tiket saat ini."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4349
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify postmaster bounces; and disables "
"sending notification if delivery fails permanently."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi bouncing postmaster; "
"dan menonaktifkan pengiriman notifikasi jika pengiriman gagal permanen."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4340
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify postmaster bounces; and handles them "
"as follow-up of the original tickets"
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi bouncing postmaster; "
"dan menanganinya sebagai tindak lanjut dari tiket asli"

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4358
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to identify postmaster bounces; and reopens "
"tickets if delivery fails permanently."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi bouncing postmaster; "
"dan membuka kembali tiket jika pengiriman gagal permanen."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4304
msgid "Defines postmaster filter to identify sender user."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi pengguna pengirim."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4295
msgid "Defines postmaster filter to identify session user."
msgstr "Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi pengguna sesi."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4457
msgid "Defines postmaster filter to identify ticket group."
msgstr "Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengidentifikasi grup tiket."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4394
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to manage Checkmk (http://mathias-kettner.com/"
"check_mk.html) emails."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengelola email Checkmk (http"
"://mathias-kettner.com/check_mk.html)."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4376
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to manage Icinga (http://www.icinga.org) emails."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengelola email Icinga "
"(http://www.icinga.org)."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4403
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to manage Monit (https://mmonit.com/monit/) emails."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengelola email Monit (https://"
"mmonit.com/monit/)."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4385
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to manage Nagios (http://www.nagios.org) emails."
msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengelola email Nagios "
"(http://www.nagios.org)."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4214
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to remove X-Zammad headers from untrustworthy "
