msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk menghapus header X-Zammad dari sumber "
"yang tidak terpercaya."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4250
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to set the owner (based on group follow up "
