msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan filter postmaster untuk mengatur pemilik (berdasarkan "
"penugasan tindak lanjut grup)."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:4259
msgid ""
"Defines postmaster filter to set the sender/from of emails based on reply-to "
