msgstr ""
"Mendefinisikan backend untuk pencarian geo IP. Juga menampilkan lokasi "
"alamat IP jika dapat dilacak."

#: db/seeds/settings.rb:480
msgid ""
"Defines the backend for geo calendar lookups. Used for initial calendar "
