#: app/assets/javascripts/app/models/trigger.coffee
msgid ""
"Every time a customer creates a new ticket, they automatically receive a "
"confirmation email to assure them that their issue has been submitted "
"successfully. This behavior is built into Zammad, but it’s also highly "
"customizable, and you can set up other automated actions just like it.\n"
"\n"
"Maybe you want to set a higher priority on any ticket with the word “urgent” "
"in the title. Maybe you want to avoid sending auto-reply emails to customers "
"from certain organizations. Maybe you want mark a ticket as “pending” "
"whenever someone adds an internal note to a ticket.\n"
"\n"
"Whatever it is, you can do it with triggers: actions that watch tickets for "
"certain changes, and then fire off whenever those changes occur."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kali pelanggan membuat tiket baru, mereka secara otomatis menerima "
"email konfirmasi untuk meyakinkan mereka bahwa masalah mereka telah berhasil "
"diserahkan. Perilaku ini dibangun ke dalam Zammad, tetapi juga sangat "
"disesuaikan, dan Anda dapat mengatur tindakan otomatis lainnya seperti itu.\n"
"\n"
"Mungkin Anda ingin menetapkan prioritas yang lebih tinggi pada setiap tiket "
"dengan kata “mendesak” dalam judul. Mungkin Anda ingin menghindari mengirim "
"email balasan otomatis ke pelanggan dari organisasi tertentu. Mungkin Anda "
"ingin menandai tiket sebagai “tergantung” setiap kali seseorang menambahkan "
"catatan internal ke tiket.\n"
"\n"
"Apa pun itu, Anda dapat melakukannya dengan pemicu: tindakan yang menonton "
"tiket untuk perubahan tertentu, dan kemudian kebakaran setiap kali perubahan "
"itu terjadi."

